it.csi.mddtools.guigen

Interface RepartModule

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    public interface RepartModule
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Repart Module'. Rappresenta un modulo di artefatti disponibile sul repository degli artefatti.

    The following features are supported:

    • Organization
    • Name
    • Version
    • Type
    • Artifacts
    See Also:
    GuigenPackage.getRepartModule()
